Variables  
==========================================================================

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jaibw/iac_tf/main/user.yaml
sed 's/my-machine-ip/<ip-address>/g' user.yaml > userfinal.yaml
ansible-playbook userfinal.yaml -e username=<any-username>

